{"tid":38612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉超市高買 休班中年女警否認控罪","createTime":"2016-12-14T04:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T06:07:18.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c147499abf00004eeae76642f010bddf87278961","tid":38612,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:46:30.000Z","msg":"一名報稱警員的中年女子涉嫌今年10月在秀茂坪商場一間超市偷竊防蚊貼、喉片等貨品，涉案貨品總值234港元，事後被控一項盜竊罪。案件今在觀塘法院再訊，女警否認控罪，案件押後至本月21日開審。<br />\n<br />\n涉案女被告黃偉芬，49歲。控方指稱被告在涉案店舖拿取涉案物品後，不付款而離開，被保安發現。警員接報拘捕被告， 警誡下表示「食咗藥唔舒服」，辯方稱將爭議被告是否有不誠實意圖。"},{"pid":"5b58e0acea7359b997ee9d5aa8f286c95c5602d3","tid":38612,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7691a507b9872abe94f7995f7714178cc73a4e","tid":38612,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:48:34.000Z","msg":"休班"},{"pid":"7984052ea029cc21f8456eafccad49be133ed94f","tid":38612,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:50:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb0ab2522524e346bbdc6cb157f36407a97ad46f","tid":38612,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:00:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">休班警員</span>"},{"pid":"274d87c8ce8cfa6ba5176db2b5518eec7f5005ed","tid":38612,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:27:36.000Z","msg":"不要搜索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227473761c42a3263fad2933abd1ed23dd59ebbe","tid":38612,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:30:31.000Z","msg":"你仆街了，遲d可能俾人告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02dba7c18932589858f4a47d6f96e64853aef214","